Ing '''matunud a kambing''' (''Capra aegagrus hircus'') ('''domestic goat''' king Ingles) metung yang subspecies ning kambing a pepatunud da manibat king [[w:wild goat|maliap a kambing]] (wild goat) ning [[w:southwest Asia|Mauli Albugang Asia]] (''Southwest Asia'') ampong [[w:Eastern Europe|Aslagang Europa]] (''Eastern Europe''). Kayabe ya ing kambing king familiang [[Bovidae]], at malapit neng kamaganak ning [[tupa]]. Pareu lang kayabe deti king [[w:goat antelope|goat antelope]] subfamily, ing [[Caprinae]].

Metung la kareng maluat nang diling pepatunud a species deng karaniwan a kambing. Pilan da nong libung banuang sesesen para king karelang [[gatas]], [[karni]], buak, ampong balat king maragul nang dake ning yatu.<ref>Coffey, Linda, Margo Hale, and Ann Wells; [http://attra.ncat.org/attra-pub/goatoverview.html "Goats: Sustainable Production Overview.]</ref> Aniang milabasan a siglu, sinikat la murin antimong sese.<ref>McLeod, Lianne; [http://exoticpets.about.com/cs/goats/a/goatsaspets.htm "Goats as Pets"] at About.com.</ref>

